Author: Alex
Message:
Merge pull request #11 from kpblcaoo/feature/dx-tool-improvements

fix: resolve test compilation errors and improve test reliability

commit 40ebf89aeb4ccf294ebde11fd5d126ecc6391962
Author: Mikhail Stepanov <kpblcaoo@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Jul 21 02:22:29 2025 +0300

fix: resolve test compilation errors and improve test reliability

- Fix MessageId property assignment in TestDataFactory (read-only property)
- Update test expectations for MessageId values (default to 0)
- Add missing WithAiChecksSetup method to MessageHandlerTestFactory
- Fix Moq setup syntax for chained method calls
- Update test logic to match actual MessageHandler flow:
  - Use IsUserApproved instead of Approved method
  - Fix exception handling expectations
  - Update captcha test to reflect actual behavior
- Use correct SpamPhotoBio type instead of AiProfileResult
- Remove optional parameters from Moq expression trees
- All 405 tests now pass successfully

Resolves compilation errors and improves test suite reliability.
